SOUNDSWIBASE                    *       &40140
SOUNDCONFIGURE                  *       SOUNDSWIBASE
SOUNDENABLE                     *       SOUNDSWIBASE+1
SOUNDSTEREO                     *       SOUNDSWIBASE+2

SOUNDCONTROL                    *       SOUNDSWIBASE+&40+6
SOUNDVOICE                      *       SOUNDSWIBASE+&40+10

SOUNDEVENTQSCHEDULE             *       SOUNDSWIBASE+&80+1
